Cases:

1. Answer once and delelete - OK
2. Answer once, accept answer and delete - OK
3. Answer twice, delete first answer, delete second answer - OK
4. Answer twice, delete second answer, delete first answer - OK
5. Answer twice, favorite first answer, delete first answer, delete second answer - OK
6. Answer twice, favorite second answer, delete first answer, delete second answer - OK
7. Answer twice, favorite first answer, delete second answer, delete first answer - OK
8. Answer twice, favorite second answer, delete second answer, delete first answer - OK

BUGS:

1. Favoriting an answer twice removes the first favorite answer